      "comment": "REBORN SCARLETT (1) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot before finishing second (29.99) and beaten 4.5 lengths over 515m at this track. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. One of the contenders. MAXIMUM GAYLE (8) comes off an average run last start when seventh at Bulli over 472m behind Al's Memory (26.98) in a Mix. Key player if finds best. GOOD ODDS KEONA (5) comes off an average run last start when fifth at this track over 515m behind Zipping Lowens (30.63) in a Grade 5. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Cannot be taken lightly. ALFIE'S PRINCESS (4) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
